{"tid":1974944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"腦退化婦身陷流浮山泥灘 一身泥救出送院不治","createTime":"2020-04-16T08:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:16:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1031b3ade69fe38a1ddc90e83a38caf8e50c050e","tid":1974944,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"中午12時許，一名老婦被發現躺在流浮山上白泥紅樹林對開50米的泥灘，全身包括臉部均沾滿泥濘，警員及消防蛙人接報到場將她救起，但據悉老婦被發現時已無呼吸脈搏，由救護車送天水圍醫院搶救，惜終告不治，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女事主為前晚在上白泥失蹤的八旬婦人。facebook專頁「香港消防救護控制組人員聯合工會」昨日貼出尋人啟事，指女事主梁娣，年約80歲，為消防員家屬，患有腦退化症及三高，前晚離開上白泥村後失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200416/6M56NIKZENBRG7XJOCVDGRI6FM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200416%2F6M56NIKZENBRG7XJOCVDGRI6FM%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c27787cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200416%2F6M56NIKZENBRG7XJOCVDGRI6FM%2F&h=7b38bd84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200416/6M56NIKZENBRG7XJOCVDGRI6FM/</a>"},{"pid":"ef79de4b8870624dc050df36a88d636bd02892b1","tid":1974944,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e4c846f9ad6ff47401879f7ccc7431bc3c54e1","tid":1974944,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"流沙好危險"},{"pid":"b75024b08d0d184874aefa595200aea622b9c295","tid":1974944,"uid":83907,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:04:00.000Z","msg":"黑警連老人都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5724727a634543b67ddbcf9067e8f04c64991c36","tid":1974944,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"可以死喺自己家鄉好幸福"},{"pid":"79374c8a118